A 3 - year - old Northwest Side girl died from multiple injuries suffered from child abuse and police are questioning a person of interest in her killing , authorities said .
The girl , identified as Ashley Mendoza , died from multiple injuries from child abuse in a homicide , the Cook County medical examiner 's office determined following an autopsy this afternoon .
